<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>IronTumblr</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bower_components/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <script src="/bower_components/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%=title%></h1>
    <h2><%=subtitle%></h2>
    <h4 class="info">Express-node.js, mongoDB-mongoose, passport...
       An user can signup and upload his avatar image, and made login and logout.
       A no logged user can also see all post and details of a post, and list existing users. Logged user can create a post with image upload, or comment it.
       If the post is own user can modify or delete it; with the elimination of image files.
    </h4>
    <h5 class="firma">By: Jorge Abad</h5>
    <br>
    <%if(typeof user!='undefined')
      {%>User logged: <b><%=user.username%></b>
        <img class="avatar" src="<%=user.profile_pic.pic_path %>" alt="">
      <%}
    %>
    <br>
    <strong>MENU</strong>
    <ul>
        <%if(typeof user === 'undefined'){%>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <li><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a></li>
            <li><a href="/listusers">List all users</a></li>
            <li><a href="/post">List all post</a></li>

        <%}else{%>
            <li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
            <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
            <li><a href="/post">List all post</a></li>
            <li><a href="/post/new">Add New post</a></li>
        <%}%>

      </ul>

    <div class="main-container">
      <%- body -%>
    </div>

    <script src="/javascripts/reward-donate.js"></script>
    <script src="/bower_components/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

  </body>
</html>
